{"tid":1434640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無唸過，其實共慘黨只係一隻紙老虎？","createTime":"2019-08-08T23:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:41:55.000Z","uid":91910,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c858c69c6b7fa058018243fae909e74db8a3721","tid":1434640,"uid":91910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"雖然共狗成日都呢樣個樣，又打經濟牌，又話出老解，但係其實點解遲遲都未出？<br />\n<br />\n按共狗邏輯，佢係唔需要同你頃，話打你就打你。全國以往好多示威，又唔見佢地搞記招？偏偏係香港，開兩次記者會。<br />\n<br />\n佢開兩次，表示佢相當重視香港，因為香港有好多高官既資產。一旦入軍，大家攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地只係講經，大港人，唔撚使驚。<br />\n<br />\n關鍵係有無香港人有同感。。。"},{"pid":"b80e785d522514fb28acf08b584428331b950a17","tid":1434640,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"我驚。<br />\n你唔知對家有咩底牌"},{"pid":"1f6a708d09b2d2f8c97e080e8385a92fb149698a","tid":1434640,"uid":269512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"當越嚟越多人醒覺嘅時候共產黨一定驚過人民，因為清算鎮壓同專政共產黨人嘅時候到了。"},{"pid":"98cb08349c1c80d965e1386849d6fbb7b3caa81d","tid":1434640,"uid":136987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:07:10.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad72c9ca7f76550ea0fe2a24d26532881e1c7f9","tid":1434640,"uid":63291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"中共今次唔可以順利咁攪香港<br />\n係因為香港嘅共產黨員不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c0ee8ce28567e83cbb6d9f538431e69ec979bf","tid":1434640,"uid":55340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"有利益價值，佢地梗係想保住<br />\n如果上海深圳一早過左香港，<br />\n香港已經係香港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港之所以咁成功，最主因係有香港人<br />\n你睇吓大陸，咁多資源，硬件軟件場地配備乜都有齊，但係點解就難以成功？運動、科研....<br />\n因為佢哋本身已經有先天缺陷，一道與世隔絕嘅屏障。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋送咗好多留學生出去，但係佢哋始終係牆入面嘅工具人，睇到嘅嘢根本唔全面，缺乏左自主思考嘅能力。"},{"pid":"3a61e3cf0b2d40f25981fd9289e874f4f07f81bc","tid":1434640,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80e785d522514fb28acf08b584428331b950a17","tid":1434640,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"我驚。<br />\n你唔知對家有咩底牌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"佢成副底牌咪係晒香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇見過人自己揸爆自己春袋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0121e5784ccb0dba2b6da2c62c8f6471973dc35b","tid":1434640,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:20:18.000Z","msg":"強大，係相對嘅<br />\n<br />\n對比香港，中國人係強大呀，不過不是戰勝。<br />\n<br />\n對比單隻細菌，人體係強大嘅，有幾十億細胞，有十大系統，有n大器官，咁點？喺周圍環境配合下，人一樣會病死。<br />\n<br />\n不過留意番，喺一個人病死前，無數細菌會死，我唔知係咪值得"},{"pid":"11fb5f7cc4a56bf38128eb423bbd098826f59143","tid":1434640,"uid":178228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a61e3cf0b2d40f25981fd9289e874f4f07f81bc","tid":1434640,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80e785d522514fb28acf08b584428331b950a17","tid":1434640,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"我驚。<br />\n你唔知對家有咩底牌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"佢成副底牌咪係晒香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇見過人自己揸爆自己春袋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"佢副底牌就係攬炒 佢寧願十三億人食樹皮食自己個仔都唔想冇面"},{"pid":"0369c13b1a0bfd92dc3c319365c8e5a6c4f30afb","tid":1434640,"uid":28358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a61e3cf0b2d40f25981fd9289e874f4f07f81bc","tid":1434640,"uid":4